2.	 In this Act, unless the context otherwise requires—
“Chairman” means the Chairman of the Authority, and includes
any temporary Chairman appointed under section 15;
“corporation” means a corporation established under section 42;
“development area” means any area in and for which a local
land development board has been established;
“Federal Land Development Authority” or “Authority” means the
Federal Land Development Authority established under section 3;
